[{"Id": 1000445, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Allama Kafmi has written this dua in his book Misbah, on the authority of Imam Ali ibne Abi Talib who learned it from the Holy Prophet. The Holy Prophet said: \"Allah will have mercy on him who keeps this dua as a taawiz, and recites it a great deal. He will forgive his sins and the sins of parents and his children, bestow on him countless blessings, keep him safe from misfortunes, multiply his earnings, and cure his ailments. \"To improve and develop memory write the (Arabic) text of this dua on a clean piece of paper with saffron, wash it with pure water and drink it. Hang the written (Arabic) text of this dua (like a taawiz) around the neck of children to keep them safe from wild and poisonous animals, and the evil of witchcraft and jinn. It is reported that at the time of meraj the Holy Prophet (a) saw this dua written at the last post, qaaba qawsayn aw adna. Allah (swt) informed him that whosoever recites this heavenly dua or keeps it written version on his person, will get countless blessings…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Allama Kafmi ne apni kitaab Misbah mein, Imam Ali (a) se riwaayat ki hai keh unho ne Rasoole Khuda (s) se suna keh, Allah (swt) us shakhs par rahem karega jo is dua ko taawiz ke taur par apne paas rakkhega aur is dua ka padhna bada ajr rakhta hai. Padhne waale ke gunah, uske maa-baap aur aulaad ke gunah bakhsh diye jaayenge, us par be-shumaar ne’mate’n naazil hongi, bala’o se mehfooz rahega, uski soonne ki quwwat badh jaayegi aur bimaari se shifa milegi. Yaad daasht ko behtar aur us mein izaafe ke liye is dua ko Arabic mein ek saaf kaagaz par zaafran se likh kar, us kaagaz ko paani se dho kar woh paani ko pee le. Is dua ko Arabic mein likh kar bachcho’n ki gardan mein baandhe, jisse woh wehshi aur zehrile jaanwaro’n se mehfooz rahega, aur jaadugar aur jinnaato’n ke sharr se bhi. Riwaayat mein hai keh, jab Rasoole Khuda (s) meraj par gaye to unho ne is dua ko aakhri hadd (qaaba qawsayn aw adna) par likkha huwa dekha. Allah (swt) ne unhe farmaaya keh jo koi is jannati dua ko padhe ya taawiz ke taur par apne paas rakkhe to usey be-shumaar ne’mate’n ataa hongi…", "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "Ara